headline: HII awarded $70M task order from U.S. Air Force
summary: HII (HII) announced that its Mission Technologies division was awarded a task order valued at approximately $70M to support the safe use of U.S. Air Force systems and software and the implementation of government-mandated information security requirements. Under the five-year task order, awarded by the U.S. Air Force Life Cycle Management Center’s Engineering Directorate, HII will identify and mitigate vulnerabilities through research and analysis to protect U.S. Air Force systems and software f
